What are you going to do

Minimum Requirements:

4+ years of software development experience with experience working in Agile teams;
Extensive experience and working knowledge of Java, object-oriented development;
Knowledge of pair programming, continuous integration and test-driven development;
Experience with at least 1 unit testing framework;
Familiarity with WebLogic Server is a plus;
Familiarity with the concepts of Micro services is a plus.


Technology Stack: Java, REST APIs, .NET (for BCAP), Spring boot, WebLogic Server, Unit testing, Performance testing and Documentation.
